values: just wanted to let u know that i am a certified massage therapist as of today. im quite excited to say the least. and very proud of myself as well.

so, umm im talking to this girl keely that i met at the mall, shes pretty interesting i like her so far. so shannon just told me that she is no longer attracted to me and that she doesnt like what we have, i was a little confused to say the least considering i just kissed her and cudled with her like yesterday but w/e. i didnt even cry, nor did i want to. and im kinda relived cause i was sweating some small shit over it and it just...well i no longer have to. i dont know how i feel about it completly just quite yet, but so far so good. im just astounded that shes not attracted to me...it makes me sad. but oh well, i hope things go well with keely, im off to bed.

so i have decided that imnot going to go into the service. well maybe but later on down the road. id really rather get a job and go to college, i want to earn my education im sick of having shit handed to me. so im going to go apply to cleaning authority tomarrow and see if that takes if not then ill look elsewhere. but i want to make a life for myself not just stock up on whats given to me and do with it as i see fit. i want to earn my place. i want to prove to myself that im not a complete fuck up and a failure at my own life. and i really have shannon to thank for my change of heart she doesnt know it but she helped me put a lot in perspective and for that i thank her. and i realize it mioght sound like im doing it for her but im not its all for me. i think shannon and i need a for real break from seeing eachother just to see if we "restart" if not then well maybe we were meant to be lovers. then itll just be a questions of us wanting eachother. but i hate the thought of doing because i feel like id just be stepping aside to let kyle step right in. i know its not how it really is but its how it feels. but yeah just figured id let you all know.

so this weekend is gunna be amazing. and my dad is leavign for a wee on sunday. im going to th ecasino for my first time and i also get a car for the WHOLE WEEK!!! becuase my dads leaving his truck here. and you can bet im gunna drive the shit out of that thing. well not really its just he doesnt let me drive it while hes home so i wanna drive it while hes gone. but i m just sooooo excited. ya know?

so i havent heard from my navy recruiter in like over a month and ive been toying with the idea of going back for the army because they are more prompt about getting you out. so i went trick or treating with jennifer last night, it was pretty fun we got a good amount of booty. lol. shes so easy to scare its funny. so the day that ends it all with shannon is drawing nearer. i saw her on monday, she got her senior pics that night, im not gunna lie it made me feel good to know i saw them before kyle and that she really missed me and wanted me to stay the night. and my phone the other night fell under my bed, how i dont know but i found two of my tarot cards which was pretty sweet. so i stopped by the school yesterday to pick jennifer up and i saw ashley and gave her a kiss and a big hug. and then i kinda lunge-kicked at shannon after doing a cartwheel. she asked me if i was ok i said i was fine and gave her a big hug. i went as a vampire, jennifer and i got my hair to stand up all over. it was amazing.but yeah i ended up talking to jessica spect yesterday and who decided to call jessica just to chit chat? the corprol. so this morning i let the dogs out and i found the corprol's card sitting on my front stoop, just chillin. and so i called him and we talked a bit it was pretty sweet. whats even better is that their moving out of the dort mall and moving near sam's club, which is quite a bit closer. but eah i just decided that fate is finally on my side i think. but now i gotta call shannon and be sure she got my message and then we have to discuss if shes going to come over tomarrow to watch beauty and the beast or not. ok, well thats all for now. buh-bye.
